short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A CoffeeScript version of the Chrome Console.
short.ja: CoffeeScript バージョンの Chrome Console。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Features:
 - Type using CoffeeScript
 - Formatted outputs
 - Auto-complete
 - Command history

Use it the way you use the original console, but with Coffee!

New in 1.2.0:
 - Update CoffeeScript to 1.7.1.
 - Add right-arrow for autocomplete.
 - Move settings icon to top-right corner.

GitHub Repository:
https://github.com/auiWorks/amCoffee
